skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: guess lucky number
des:
Guess A Number is an interesting number game in which you have to predict the number between 1 to 100. Say Alexa open guess the number and it will ask you whether you want to play or not. then it will guide you to the correct number.
You:- Open guess a number
Alexa:- Would you like to play
You:- Yes
.
.
You:- three
Alexa:- three is too low.
You:- twenty two 
Alexa:- twenty two is too high
You:- twenty one
Alexa:- 22 is correct answer. would you like to play again?

Enjoy the game and do rate and review.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
